{"tid":1981653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"過去2小時已經2宗墮樓案","createTime":"2020-04-20T19:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:39:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c5a6a414b3b299a778d7fc30119f9c6fd3320f","tid":1981653,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"今日(21日)凌晨1時許，一名年約50歲的男子從上環蘇杭街92號大廈高處墮下，他重傷昏迷倒臥馬路邊，途人見狀報案。男事主由救護員送院搶救，惜終告返魂乏術。警方初步調查，在死者身上無檢獲身份證明文件，惟得悉他並非上址住客，並由天台墮下，正跟進其身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n一名女子於今日(21日)凌晨2時許，倒臥在上水彩園邨彩華樓對開重創昏迷，流出大量鮮血，途人發現大驚報案求助。救護員趕至證實女子當場死亡，並由警員用帳篷將遺體遮蓋；經調查相信女事主從彩華樓飛墮而下，正就其墮樓原因展開跟進。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 方向唔貼LINK"},{"pid":"f585606f06fa2102129fe3769b74d59b9629d770","tid":1981653,"uid":320074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=8b7783dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span sty